Installation
------------

To install, use

  $ pip install txretry

or if you're not a fan of pip:

  $ python setup.py install  # You may need sudo.

If you want to install in a virtualenv:

  $ virtualenv --no-site-packages env
  $ . env/bin/activate
  $ pip install -r requirements.txt

Running the tests
-----------------

  $ trial txretry
